getResolution

public byte getResolution()
The resolution of the Band specification. "1" resolution = 0 // the whole chromosom "1p" resolution = 1 // the whole arm "1p22" resolution = 2 // band "1p22.3" resolution = 3 // subband "Yq12a" "1p22.3e" resolution = 4 // subsubband
